sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as System Administrator
    participant Discovery as Discovery Engine (DDG/RSS)
    participant Crawler as Autonomous Multi-modal Crawler
    participant Extractor as Extraction Layer (Docling/Trafilatura)
    participant NLP as Joint NLP Pipeline (Mistral)
    participant DB as Unified Storage (Mongo/Neo4j)

    Admin->>Discovery: Configure Topics (Politics, Finance, etc.)
    
    par Multi-Format Discovery
        Discovery->>Crawler: Web Article URLs
        Discovery->>Crawler: PDF Report URLs
        Discovery->>Crawler: Video Transcript Links
    end

    loop Process Stream
        alt Format: HTML
            Crawler->>Extractor: Trafilatura (Clean Text)
        else Format: PDF
            Crawler->>Extractor: Docling (Structured Markdown/Tables)
        else Format: Video/Audio
            Crawler->>Extractor: Whisper/Transcript Processor
        end
        
        Extractor-->>Crawler: Normalized Markdown Content
        
        Crawler->>NLP: Unified Textual Input
        activate NLP
        Note over NLP: Joint Entity, Relation & Stance Extraction
        NLP-->>Crawler: Structured Geopolitical Triples
        deactivate NLP
        
        Crawler->>DB: Persist (Raw Metadata + Graph Topology)
    end
